and the doctor says he's got,
he's got... he's like, um, he's...

28:27.539 --> 28:31.751
he's affected by light,
and he has a neck injury.

28:31.835 --> 28:36.214
Well, the neck... the neck
didn't start hurting him until Friday

28:36.297 --> 28:38.925
and he told me that
it was how he slept on it.

28:39.008 --> 28:40.677
-Mmm.
-[chuckles] So, I mean...

28:40.760 --> 28:42.887
