28:54.441 --> 28:57.152
So, well, when he comes outside,
he says... he says he's...

28:57.235 --> 28:59.112
he says he's, uh...

28:59.195 --> 29:01.406
When he goes outside, he's, uh...

29:01.489 --> 29:03.742
Hey! Let's go, Tyree!

29:05.076 --> 29:08.079
