he'd been in his room, he goes outside...

29:08.163 --> 29:11.583
the light makes him... hurts his eyes.

29:11.666 --> 29:14.711
Hell yeah, when you been
layin' up in a cold room,

29:14.794 --> 29:17.130
-sleeping all day. You go outside...
-[laughs]

29:20.967 --> 29:23.136
[Wagner] Ollie.
What're... what're you doing?

29:23.845 --> 29:25.513
What're you doing?

29:30.935 --> 29:32.395
What the hell?

29:35.356 --> 29:36.816
