[line ringing]

30:01.591 --> 30:05.178
[automated voice] <i>I'm sorry, but</i>
<i>the person you called has a voicemail box</i>

30:05.261 --> 30:07.013
<i>-that has not been set up yet.</i>
-[sighs] Damn it.

30:07.096 --> 30:08.723
Answer the phone.

30:14.479 --> 30:16.064
-[line beeps]
-Oh, my gosh.

30:16.147 --> 30:18.274
I'm really gonna freaking
drive over to your dorm.

30:24.030 --> 30:25.949
-I don't understand.
-[cell phone chimes]

30:26.032 --> 30:27.909
Oh, hold on, hold on.

30:27.992 --> 30:31.579
"Man, Coach Stephens talking crazy to me

30:31.663 --> 30:37.544
