I just want attention.

30:38.586 --> 30:42.549
Man, I did every fucking thing
possible to satisfy y'all. Every..."

30:42.632 --> 30:43.842
Whoa!

30:43.925 --> 30:47.679
"Every motherfucking thing
y'all asked me to do, I've done.

30:47.762 --> 30:50.515
