<i>The minute that Ollie feels</i>
<i>threatened or called out,</i>

31:03.862 --> 31:06.573
<i>I mean, his reaction</i>
<i>is to just either flee</i>

31:06.656 --> 31:09.659
<i>or he's gonna go right back at you.</i>
