<i>like, that's kind of</i>
<i>abandonment in his eyes.</i>

31:27.594 --> 31:30.138
<i>So then, it's like</i>
<i>he's got to do something to see...</i>

31:30.221 --> 31:33.558
<i>Is everybody that he,</i>
<i>that he cares about abandoning him or,</i>

