[Ollie] Hey!

35:02.642 --> 35:04.769
[blows raspberry]

35:04.852 --> 35:06.104
-What up?
-[Takesha] Say hey.

35:06.187 --> 35:07.271
[both chuckle]

35:08.231 --> 35:09.398
[babbling]

35:09.482 --> 35:11.192
-[both chuckle]
-Finna' go bye-bye?

35:11.275 --> 35:13.361
-You finna' go?
-Yeah!

35:15.113 --> 35:16.906
[Takesha] All right be easy, then.

35:16.989 --> 35:19.117
Don't be out all night, my God.

35:19.200 --> 35:20.201
[indistinct chatter]

35:21.119 --> 35:22.995
