-He really gonna put us on the map.
-Yep.

37:02.220 --> 37:04.639
[Devontae] <i>He really gonna make</i>
<i>something happen for this little school.</i>

37:04.722 --> 37:05.890
[Stalexus] <i>Yep.</i>

