<i>Fires it over the middle.</i>
<i>And it's, uh... it's off his fingertips.</i>

38:47.491 --> 38:50.828
<i>And it's gonna be Northeast's football</i>
<i>after the turnover on downs.</i>

38:50.911 --> 38:53.205
[Buddy] <i>What in the fuck!</i>
<i>Come here!</i>

