Okay, give me the... Hey!

39:19.815 --> 39:21.901
Go to, uh... Hey!
Where you at? Where you at?

39:21.984 --> 39:22.985
Where you at?
Go to center.

39:23.069 --> 39:24.653
Go to center.
Go to center.

