39:42.671 --> 39:44.423
No, that ain't what I said.

39:55.059 --> 39:56.936
[Buddy] <i>Ooh-wee. I ain't pleased.</i>

39:57.019 --> 39:59.397
[stuttering] <i>I mean,</i>
<i>we're not playin' very well.</i>

39:59.480 --> 40:01.440
<i>You know, we're not playin'</i>
<i>with our mind in the game.</i>

