<i>It's one quarter of execution</i>
<i>and one quarter of non-execution.</i>

40:04.026 --> 40:06.237
<i>So, we're not as good</i>
<i>as what we think we are.</i>

40:06.320 --> 40:08.864
<i>So, uh, we gotta do a little better job</i>
<i>on coachin',</i>

40:08.948 --> 40:11.242
<i>we gotta do a little better job</i>
<i>on execution,</i>

40:11.325 --> 40:13.202
and we gotta go out and play
with attitude in the second half.

40:13.285 --> 40:14.870
-All right, Coach, thanks.
