or I'll rip them motherfuckers off.

40:23.546 --> 40:25.214
Get 'em off.
Get 'em off.

40:26.382 --> 40:28.551
Look at me like that
your ass'll damn walk home.

40:29.510 --> 40:31.345
Dropping fuckin' balls.

40:31.429 --> 40:33.681
Griping and complaining
about not damn startin'.

40:33.764 --> 40:36.183
Catch a damn ball.
Make a damn play.

40:36.267 --> 40:37.435
[player] All right, man.

40:37.518 --> 40:39.145
Shut the fuck up!

40:39.228 --> 40:41.272
Don't say a goddamn word to me!

40:42.648 --> 40:44.191
That's what I fuckin' think.

40:45.359 --> 40:47.695
Too many damn people think
they got this shit made

40:47.778 --> 40:50.573
'cause they played on last year's team.
Fuck that!

